node.text: The new album is named for West’s late mother, who passed away in 2007. While DONDA explores a wider range of genres than his previous album Jesus is King, it features some of the religious themes that West has pivoted to in his recent music. A partial tracklist posted by West ahead of the release listed titles like “Pure Souls” and “Keep My Spirit Alive.” The album will be available for purchase and streaming on July 23rd.

node.text: Founded by Jeff Bezos, space travel company Blue Origin completed its first passenger flight on July 20. The rocket, named New Shepard, carried Bezos and three other passengers more than 65-miles above Earth, just to the boundary of space, known as the Kármán line. Watch our latest episode of HBNN to learn more.

node.title: @jeffbezos Completes His First Flight into Space

#hypeAF: @lego is celebrating season 2 of @themandalorian with a 1336-piece Imperial Light Cruiser model. The piece is loaded with two spring-loaded rotating turrets, two mini TIE Fighters, and a launcher, alongside five LEGO mini-figures featuring The Mandalorian, Cara Dune, Fennec Shand, Moff Gideon, a Dark Trooper and Baby Yoda. Find it now on LEGO’s website for $159.99 USD.⁠⁠
Photo: LEGO
